Find users who have a 'Subscribe' event but NO 'Cancel' event.
subscriptions( user_id INT, event TEXT, event_date TEXT )
Sample Input
user_id	event	event_date
1	Subscribe	2024-01-01
2	Subscribe	2024-01-02
2	Cancel	2024-02-01
3	Subscribe	2024-01-10
Expected Output
user_id
1
3
SELECT DISTINCT s1.user_id
FROM subscriptions s1
WHERE s1.event = 'Subscribe'
AND NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1 
    FROM subscriptions s2 
    WHERE s2.user_id = s1.user_id 
    AND s2.event = 'Cancel'
);

